he knowledge must be GENERAL > (many domains, each phrased for ALL instances of that domain) and carry **ZERO scenario literals** > (no persona/place/fixture) — a domain-keyed knowledge base is the RIGHT home for domain-flavored > guidance that would be overfitting inside a system-wide prompt. A partition/classification rule > that keeps failing as prose is itself the signal to climb to this rung.  **L3 FRAMEWORK GAP** — today's pr","stderr":"","interrupted":false,"isImage":false,"noOutputExpected":false,"persistedOutputPath":"/home/vasilis/.claude/projects/-home-vasilis-LMTHING-lmthing/4abecf79-4263-4bbb-a5c4-a77231683cc7/tool-results/bglon7gkf.txt","persistedOutputSize":71240}}
